| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2927 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 17e77ec8-418a-5b48-be53-1f9b23a06b0c"
